        article.services
            h2 
                span BRAND   
                span SERVICES
            p We are one of the biggest creative team and we have been helping our clients solve problems with branding and we always provide the best service for their businesses 
            
            div.cards
                div.card_service
                    h3 MARKETING
                    ul 
                        li SEO, site promotion
                        li Contextual advertising
                        li SMM
                        li Advertising in social networks
                        li Development of loyalty programs
                div.card_service
                    h3 BRANDING
                    ul 
                        li Market analysis and CA
                        li Development strategy
                        li Brand positioning
                        li Naming, the legend of the brand
                        li Development of a logo, brand book
                div.card_service
                    h3 PR
                    ul 
                        li Definition of the goal and CA
                        li Reputation building
                        li PR
                        li SERM
                        li Building and realise PR campaign
                div.card_service
                    h3 OTHER SERVICES
                    ul 
                        li Strategic sessions
                        li Design
